name: Jakarta: Happy Ending
description: This photo was inspired by the song "Jam Makan Siang" (Lunch Time) by Hindia ft. Matter Mos. This song represents my feelings while working in Jakarta. Every lunch with office friends, there is always a conversation about the boss's behaviour, complicated life problems, and our dreams for life in future. We also realized, a struggle as we work, we are only preparing money for our graves and happy endings.
